    {
      "id": "step-8-full-picture",
      "title": "The Full Picture",
      "description": "Here's the complete data flow: a user prompt enters through the web client (or a bot integration), hits the control plane Durable Object over WebSocket, which provisions a sandbox on the data plane. Streaming events flow back through the same WebSocket chain. The shared package ties all TypeScript services together, and Terraform deploys everything. Check the resources below for the deep architecture dive.",
      "estimatedTime": 30,
      "focusDirectory": "",
      "colorMode": "fileTypes",
      "highlightLayers": [
        {
          "id": "tier-web",
          "name": "Tier 1: Web Client",
          "color": "#3b82f6",
